-- Orlando Magic Sign Coach Stan Van Gundy to Contract Extension Through 2013
-- Jay Beberman
-- 2010-07-28T14:39:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/orlando-magic-sign-coach-stan-van-gundy-to-contract-extension-through-2013.html

          
          
             The Orlando Magic signed coach Stan
Van Gundy to a contract extension through the 2012-13 season,
the National Basketball Association team said in a statement.  
 Since Van Gundy joined Orlando, the Magic have won three
consecutive Southeast Division titles and advanced to the NBA
Finals during the 2008-09 season.  
          
          


  


        